                <h2>Hangman GUI</h2>
                <p>
                    A hangman game using Windows Forms in C#. The textbox allows for user input of one character at a time or the full word
                    as a valid guess. Either way can be used to solve the puzzle but an incorrect word or character guess is counted as a
                    wrong guess. Invalid input of special characters brings up a dialog box but is not counted against the user. The game includes
                    sound effects for wrong guesses and when the user wins or looses the game.
                </p>
