                <h2>Cheese Finder</h2>
                <p>
                    The goal of the game is collect as much cheese as possible without getting caught by a cat. There are three
                    different types of cat(@@) indicated by their color:
                    <span style="color:lawngreen;background-color:black">Kitten</span> <span style="color:yellow;background-color:black">Housecat</span> <span style="color:red;background-color:black">Tiger</span>.
                    The kitten doesn't move often and can only move in four directions. The housecat moves more often and can move in all
                    eight directions. The tiger moves nearly every turn in all eight directions and is very hard to get away from. All cats use a basic
                    pathfinding algorithm to seek out the mouse. Also, the mouse has to eat cheese to keep itself from running out of energy which can kill it.
                </p>
